docs.title: GET /users/{userId}
docs.text:
Get user by ID

Input parameters

Parameter In Type Default Nullable Description userId path integer No

Response 200 OK

application/json 
{
    "id": 123,
    "name": "Jane Doe",
    "email": "jane@example.com"
}
Schema of the response body 
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "id": {
            "type": "integer"
        },
        "name": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "email": {
            "type": "string"
        }
    }
}

Response 404 Not Found

application/json 
{
    "message": "User not found"
}
Schema of the response body 
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "message": {
            "type": "string"
        }
    }
}
